  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="8325459">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/8325459/" class="title-link">辛亥革命中模糊不清的立宪派</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-8325459"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/45410430/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u45410430-8.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/45410430/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">代洲</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2017-01-31"
      class="main-meta">2017-01-31 09:12:23</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_8325459_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  中学历史教科书对于立宪派只是一笔带过，提到了他们上书请愿开国会，之后在辛亥革命中似乎就消失了。那么，立宪派到底在革命过程中起了何种作用，这是本书希望回答的问题。 本书初版于1969年，距离辛亥革命已近60年，此时可以更加清晰地分析立宪派在辛亥革命过程中的作用。同时...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 0没用</span>
                        <span class="publisher left">
                            三辉图书/上海三联书店2013版</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_8325459_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_8325459_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
